Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, help yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is perfect! Absolutely perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could serve this up at the shop. In fact, why don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lan, won't you have some?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got too much on my mind right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess my plan didn't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I made this breakfast for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We live under the same roof, but Lan still won't open up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping this would give us a chance to get to know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you've been up since three in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I knew that would only upset you, Lan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you're a very honest person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural that you'd get mad at being dragged into a friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I realized that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.90,0:05:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will? Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I ate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I didn't hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,How do you like living with Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,Oh, it's just too much fun! Right, Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}It seems you're having a hard time dealing with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}She took me by surprise this morning, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Did you learn anything about Muginami?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No, there is no data in Le Garite matching her description either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:05:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Any connection with the escaped prisoner?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nothing. We don't even know how that one managed to escape in the first place.
