Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:06.26,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\xshad-1\blur1\fs37\bord0\fnPoor Richard\c&HF0FFFC&\4c&H67A134&\pos(757,263)}Horoscope
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:06.30,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\xshad-2\blur1\fs50\bord0\fnPoor Richard\c&HF0FFFC&\4c&H67A134&\pos(808,217)}Horoscope
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:06.34,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\xshad-2\blur1\fs60\bord0\fnPoor Richard\c&HF0FFFC&\4c&H67A134&\pos(843,191)}Horoscope
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:06.38,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\xshad-2\blur1\fs68\bord0\fnPoor Richard\c&HF0FFFC&\4c&H67A134&\pos(866,172)}Horoscope
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:06.42,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\xshad-2\blur1\fs74\bord0\fnPoor Richard\c&HF0FFFC&\4c&H67A134&\pos(883,161)}Horoscope
