Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:07.76,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\blur0.5\fs33\fnGeorgia\pos(678,274)\c&H4A3A26&}Weekly: Cancer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It says Cancers have to be patient this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Due to Pluto being in retrograde..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder bad things keep happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better limit myself to two yogurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continue checking the Le Garite database records on Muginami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact me if you learn anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.19,0:06:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? It's your turn at bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you get for scheming during class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get revenge for Lan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get any closer to Muginami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a danger to you, Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind that cheerful demeanor,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she's scheming something very frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.95,0:07:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.78,0:07:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muginami is a nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.03,0:07:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember how she rescued you, Lan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she did, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.61,0:07:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm sure even that was part of her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she just hit a home run for you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means she's your comrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave it up to your judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we really use this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see... it's a storeroom, but yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think this place is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.95,0:08:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're done, be sure to return it to the faculty office.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyono!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're one step ahead of Yoko. Keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! A room for our club!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's all thanks to you two joining the club!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess we should start acting more like Sweats Club members, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Student Council requested help with moving some of their stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muginami and I will handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Madoka, you can take care of the groceries that Mr. Hiroshi asked for. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll leave the rest to you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woof.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to lock up afterwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.22,0:09:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't forget to lock up afterwards."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I sound like a club captain or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Energy replenished!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight I'll make a jumbo-size fish sandwich just like Uncle taught me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that coat looks better on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, how many times we gotta go through this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? We did?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then the next coat on sale is—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:09:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Madoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my niece. Isn't she cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Giovu... Aw man, I bit my tongue again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drinking out here, in broad daylight? How bold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well actually, he and I had bit of an argument earlier and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our way of making up! Yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want a drink too, Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got everything except the soy sauce and sugar. Now go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.26,0:10:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.93,0:10:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka, I don't think you should be wearing anything besides white—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've been to this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I've been walking around to see the sights.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to say the ocean view from here is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thank you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what did you and my uncle argue about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there was only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to argue
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,over something if it's just lying around, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't we supposed to help out the student council?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you hope to gain by getting close to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering when you'd ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lan, all you ever did was observe me from the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yours is here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you have the Memoria?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so hard about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just stood naked in front of the Vox and then it poked me.{uh}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you intend to do with the Vox?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. Ask Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother said he wanted it, that's why I came to get this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know the horror that the Vox is capable of!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about the "Legend of the Demons"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard that it's really, really scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's just an old fairy tale, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, did you tell Madoka about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave Madoka out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh, so you haven't told her yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, Lan, is that really a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell Madoka when the time comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I have a suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother will be coming to this town soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, he should be here anytime now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then this town will become a battlefield for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you have your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that why there's going to be a war?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, war between us is inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's enjoy this while we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant our student life here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just confirmed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Like she said, Ignis has undergone Memoria.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}How could that happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}And as for "Brother"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What did you learn?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}The same as Muginami.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.79,0:14:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}There isn't a criminal that matches up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Then it must be a codename.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Listen, find out who this "Brother" is, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Brother"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Welcome back. You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You have a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Giuvi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.86,0:14:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Villa. Villagiulio.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:14:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a token of my apology for upsetting Madoka,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I helped her pick up trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she said she'd treat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just said we deserve to have some good food after picking up all that trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so late!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just knew you'd come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muginami,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is he your older brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we're not related,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.55,0:15:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Brother"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.06,0:15:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Laffinty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:15:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's our enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:15:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Shabada—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Giuvi—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Villagiulio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about Muginami?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's also our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she doesn't seem that way at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that you're our enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Lan say so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys who came to attack us last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they also your people, Muginami?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they're—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not your enemy, Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on Brother's side. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means you're the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe to you, Lan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this doesn't involve Madoka, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we're the ones at war.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say this doesn't involve me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it involves me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:16:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We live together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We go to school together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same club together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how can you say this doesn't involve me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just go around having fun
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you and Lan are fighting right in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was pretty fun for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike Lan over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we all woke up in the morning and ate breakfast,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.53,0:17:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and went to school and gossiped, then ate again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the afternoon, as we listened to the teacher's lecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we took a quick nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we did Sweats Club activities until evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we went home and helped at the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we took a leisurely bath and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,slept 'til the next morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did the same thing every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'd never had such an easy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved every minute of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why I told Lan earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to have to fight sooner or later,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we should enjoy this life while we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.05,0:18:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Lan got upset and told me to quit fooling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you, Muginami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that's the way you thought about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I really did have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I honestly wished these days could continue for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Lan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please understand, Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And wake me up when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:18:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:19:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, back to Kiss where everyone's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.28,0:19:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the name of their organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when did you become one of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't pilot an Ovid,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nor can you handle a gun properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.58,0:19:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you do is eat and sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We put our lives on the line fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while you've had it nice and easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have some nerve calling yourself one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this. I have the Memoria for the Vox.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why aren't you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you were talking with everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:19:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About taking possession of the Vox—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You took the remaining Vox for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell asked you to do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.89,0:20:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think that would make you one of us? Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think that would make up for all the free meals you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me "Brother". It's "Lord Villagiulio".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're a parasite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.29,0:20:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop me, Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This jerk! This jerk just called Muginami a...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.27,0:21:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laffinty...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Moid this message:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy every Vox in your possession by tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.84,0:21:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy them along with that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is just like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.22,0:21:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurikano.
